  "body": "The [pod description](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/docs/user-guide/persistent-volumes/simpletest/pod.yaml#L15) of the persistent-volumes walkthrough contains the volume mount `/var/www/html` which seems to be outdated for the used nginx conatiner which is by default serving from the `/usr/share/nginx/html` folder.\n\nAs a result, the data wrtitten in `/var/www/html` in the node will not be returned by the `curl` at the end of the walkthought.\n\nProposed change: Update the path\n",
